 microprocessors. </p>
<p>

CapROS is being <link>
developed</link> by Strawberry Development Group with funding from the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../957/8957.xml">
Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency</link>. The primary developer is <link>
Charles Landau</link>.</p>

